Masihlole izitatimende ezimbili ngokwahlukana:

Isitatimende 1: (ab)^{-2} = b^{-2}a^{-2}

Oku yiqiniso. Ngokwesibonelo:
Makube (ab)^{-2} = (ab)^{-1} × (ab)^{-1}
= (a^{-1}b^{-1}) × (a^{-1}b^{-1}) (Ngokusebenzisa isibonelo (xy)^{-1} = x^{-1}y^{-1})
= a^{-1}a^{-1} × b^{-1}b^{-1}
= a^{-2} × b^{-2}
= b^{-2}a^{-2}

Ngakho-ke, isitatimende 1 siyiqiniso.

Isitatimende 2: (ab)^n = a^nb^n

Oku yiqiniso futhi. Ngokwesibonelo:
(ab)^n = (ab × ab × ... × ab) (n amathemu)
= (a × a × ... × a) × (b × b × ... × b) (Ngokusebenzisa isibonelo (xy)^n = x^ny^n)
= a^n × b^n

Ngakho-ke, isitatimende 2 siyiqiniso.

Ngakho-ke, impendulo elungile ithi: A. Yiqiniso, Yiqiniso
